Runtime support

Detailed Description

The 'rt_' prefix for functions in this file stands for 'runtime' - the methods with this prefix are intended for the support of the compiled method during runtime.


Modules

 General execution support
 
Note:
Most of 'rt_' functions here (except of rt_check_method) expect that the method passed as argument was indeed compiled by the Jitrino.JET.
